com.sap.spe.condmgnt.customizing

Interface IAttributeMap

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface IAttributeMap
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface for an attributeMap-object. The access contains a list of attributeMaps. This attributeMap-object contains the mapping between attributes of the (sales) document and the key fields of the condition table which is assigned to the access.
